column6: Collecting the l tales that took Marvel.com storm, these digital divas are coming at your courtesy of comics' hottest writers and the superstar artists of tomorrow. In this opening salvo, a young Medusa learns that family makes the fiercest foes, Enchantress faces stiff competition from a shocking X-enemy, and the Black Cat finds the only thing standing between her and a shiny gem is (EEK!) the Devil's Daughter'SATANA!! Rated T  '$3.99
